title: Who deserves to be in the MLS Best XI? | Futbol Americas | ESPN FC

media:group.media:title: Who deserves to be in the MLS Best XI? | Futbol Americas | ESPN FC
media:group.media:description:
ESPN FC’s Sebastian Salazar and Herculez Gomez discuss if they agree with Diego Fagúndez being displeased with MLS’ MVP choice on Futbol Americas. Seb questions the process as he doesn’t understand why the likes of Javier Hernández and Cristian Arango are nominated but don’t end up on the Best XI.
